Changelog
*********

1.2.1 (2019-01-25)
==================

Bug Fixes
---------

- Fixed ``install_requires`` option of ``setup.py``.

1.2.0 (2019-01-22)
==================

Changes
-------

- Added checking of version of python in exists venv directory and
  recreate venv if the version is not equal to current python version.

